          <p>The Other Activities and Organizations series is divided into four subseries, Civic Interests, Musical Material, Radio Material, and Photographs. The Civic Interests subseries consists of material related to Detroit city and neighborhood organizations and issues. The Musical subseries contains material documenting Gajec's involvement in musical organizations, education, and businesses. It includes concert programs, papers from the bands Gajec led or performed with, professional correspondence, and musical education material. The Radio subseries contains publicity material and memoranda from Detroit radio stations. The Photographs subseries contains undated unidentified photographs of musical and theatrical subjects.</p>
        </scopecontent>
